dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew 铁工会
dataList.content: What d’we have ‘ere? 这是什么？

dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew 铁工会
dataList.content: D’you fellers have any idea what you’ve just walked into? 你们这帮人知道自己刚刚闯进了什么地方吗？

dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew 铁工会
dataList.content: Try mucking about and we’ll make the most acrobatic poses known to man outta you. 如果你敢胡闹，我们会把你变成被人类知道的最灵活的姿势。

dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew 铁工会
dataList.content: Then we’ll lop off your digits joint by joint and make purdy mahjong tiles with ‘em. 然后我们会一个关节一个关节地砍掉你的指头，用它们做成漂亮的麻将牌。
Sheesh… Some warm welcome that was. 唉……这真是个热烈的欢迎。
Feh, I’m not one to let introductions like that go unanswered. Oi! Dust up! 呸，我可不是那种让这种介绍无人回应的人。喂！准备打架吧！
